title: Ep. 536 - Tapu's Great Decision - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal is tensed and rushes home. Iyer, Babita, and Bhide wonder what is wrong with Jethalal. Tapu decided to shave his head and go bald. Jethalal and Daya try to make him change his mind.

title: Ep. 537 - A Bald Situation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu's decision affects all the kids in the society. All the kids want to go bald. The parents try to make their kids understand but the situation gets out of hand and Tapu goes bald.

title: Ep. 538 - A Bold Step Of Getting Bald - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu gets Bald despite everyone in the society requesting him to keep his beautiful hair.  He proudly flaunts his bald head and refuses to give any reason for taking the step. As per Anjali's plan, Anjali, Tarak, Jethalal and Daya follow Tapu.

title: Ep. 539 - A Proud Moment For Everyone - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal, Daya, Anjali and Tarak finds out that Tapu got bald to support his friend who has leukaemia and this makes them extremely proud. Later, all the men of the Gokuldham society decide to party at Popat's house in the evening.

title: Ep. 540 - The Values Of Life And Friendship - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The party gets canceled as Champaklal suddenly returns from his pilgrimage which makes the men sad. However, the men of Gokuldham society realize how much they value each other as friends.

title: Ep. 541 - Tapu's Prank - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide, impressed by Tapu, decides to give him a gift but in return, gets pranked by him. Bhide aware everybody at the society to get ready for the upcoming census as two officers are scheduled to visit the society on the next day.

title: Ep. 542 - The Census Operation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide takes his former teacher, Mr. Deshpande, and Mr. Pandey across the society for the Census Operation. Although the residents cooperate with the gentlemen a lot, they force Mr. Deshpande and Mr. Pandey to have breakfast.

title: Ep. 543 - The Ugly Fight - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal is worried about the huge bill payments. Soon Jethalal and Mr. Iyer get into an ugly fight. Everyone in the society asks them not to fight else they won't be in talking terms with both of them. Later, Madhvi informs Daya about the fight.

title: Ep. 544 - The Story Of Umbrella - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal decides to switch sim card and went on to meet Jethalal. Meanwhile Jethalal asks him the reason for him carrying an umbrella in winters and he started narrating why.

title: Ep. 545 - The Misunderstanding And Missed Call Alerts - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: As Vaijayanti had instructed Popatlal to give her a missed call on a given number, later, it turns out Babita owns that number. He kept on giving missed calls thinking Babita to be Vaijayanti. Here, Babita and Mr. Iyer decide to file FIR.

title: Ep. 546 - A Ceremony For World Cup - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone in Gokuldham discusses on World cup that would start the next day. Tapu comes up with the idea of keeping hawan so that India wins the World cup this time. Everyone wears masks of the cricketers and come for the Hawan.

title: Ep. 547 - Mr. Iyer In Doubt - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita is still worried about the missed calls. Mr. Iyer doubts Jethalal which is why he visits his house to get some proof only to find out that Jethalal was not the one doing it. Later, Mr. Iyer gets to know he uses two mobile phones.

title: Ep. 548 - Jethalal Has No Bad Intentions - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Mr. Iyer still doubts Jethalal's intentions. He follows Jethalal till his shop and was looking for a chance to know if he was the one who disturbed Babita throughout the night. Mehta infoms Jethalal about Iyer's speculations about him.

title: Ep. 549 - The Missed Call - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All the ladies of Gokuldham call on the unknown number and ask him to meet. Here, Popatlal is all set to meet Vaijayanti. The whole society, Gokuldham, goes together to know who that missed call guy is.

title: Ep. 550 - Everyone In Confusion - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Finally the confusion is cleared. Popatlal describes how he thought that Vaijayanti likes him and had given her number to him. Babita clears the confusion in numbers.
